Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信也要去久間田？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟慧的娘家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧的臉色真可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我的身體是可以隨便穿過的也用不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖分比想像之中吸收得要多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年再試一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很健康地活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣或許會好一些吧…你不覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望你快點到繼承酒場的年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一起聽爵士樂就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我也越來越老了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你會這樣想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  不要再跟你媽媽說那種奇怪的話了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  你也在用你自己的方式關心你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧的新酒怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的酵母菌吃掉了過多的米糖分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的…酵母菌？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是養得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是太過亢奮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個酵母菌…是我嚇到他們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  失敗是成功之母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧作為杜氏也得到經驗教訓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去一趟慧那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧回久間田了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才她說要向爺爺匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我覺得我必須向慧道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信為什麼要去久間田呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去見媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐死了  但是說不定卻轉生成為了另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那難道是都？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知為何一直對那個女孩十分在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這或許就是緣由  這種念頭一直纏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼家裡那個叫{\u1}加畑{\r}的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我婆婆死了以後還在家裡賴著不走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在盤算著什麼邪惡的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神拜靈會？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺可疑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…雖然我覺得和我目前的目標完全沒有聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  00－02
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份禮我總有一天會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？這邊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  就是大壩的屍體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不是日本人了吧  通過DNA鑑定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DBI（大日本生物）裡頭吸納了國內外很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有什麼「友田三傑」麼  要解散了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼  反正我提供的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一橋那邊都只是被整理成檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  都要代替大神婆婆而成為「審神巫女」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會容許的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你還在那裡  信你要去哪兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用「言靈」殺死了婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（言靈：語言內在的神靈，語言所具有的力量）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概「逆風」就快要發生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（逆風：使用某種法術之後帶來的逆反應）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「逆風」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說詛咒會遭到報應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是被一言主神附身了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼給縣裡宣傳取材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這理由還真是老掉牙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向我問話的時候  也淨是問了奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…其實啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給縣裡頭的宣傳部打電話一問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答說在這水天鎮裡頭可沒什麼常駐採訪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊  我們也沒打算把你的事情捅到哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有很多想知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來一次Give and Take啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是要交換訊息？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來過？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去慧那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信你要去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？陪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要去道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比慧早一代的杜氏  也就你爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  又叫「久間田杜氏」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前起這裡出身的杜氏都很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  挺不錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天鎮也是這個樣子  久間田也沒什麼區別嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信以前來過久間田？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我還是個沒有記憶的小孩的時候來過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  我最早的記憶是幾歲來著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個事件發生的時候  記憶應該還沒有完善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的事情  我卻清清楚楚地記得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…今天是3月22日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的夢  還是在龜岩大壩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫院裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐一直在說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…不管我怎麼喊  她都不睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點累了  好像有點想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…難道…我生姐姐氣的時候  跑到在小學裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  不要哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…聽不到  太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎你一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…不知為什麼對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭克斯坦教授  要是你能早點給我研究訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的家就不會分崩離析了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠實地說  我屬於司法部機關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個不怎麼能隨便張揚的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們也要替我保守這個秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這個鎮是為了調查大日本生物公司的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是說他們在這兒做什麼危險的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這個研究所對日本的國家利益十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論國內國外  很多情報機關試圖竊取訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  正如你們剛才所問  在大壩死掉的那個人大概是商業間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸究竟在研究什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是什麼都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒跟老爸認真談過話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這年紀也該是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  特意跑來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這是信  中學裡的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他啊  最近身體不大好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就讓我回來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是上了年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事必須向慧道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎你？是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧好像在試驗新的酵母菌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽爸爸說失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那件事啊  是我沒釀好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我進了發酵室  把那些酵母菌嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒的鎖…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替他開的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替他開的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是錯的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是想進去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著新生命不斷誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那是多麼有趣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這肯定嚇到那些酵母菌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  反正社長也原諒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是從前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人的氣息進入發酵室  那杜氏就要被炒魷魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧及時停止了  沒什麼太大的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且玄米酒比去年好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算下週回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞你特意來久間田一趟  真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信也請
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  網路狀況不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我看看路由器跑得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這屋子真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是匡幸的爸爸  科學家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我這邊的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信你要去哪兒  我也陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  太郎你還是早點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係  我陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真謝謝你  幫了大忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說算了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你要去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信大人  雖然姬大人已經仙逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大神拜靈會將繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是比以前更進一步地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像姬大人年輕時候的那樣繼續繁榮下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡怎麼樣就怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在信大人願意繼承這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將在此侍奉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種時候絕對不會有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  要是你再敢對龜岩神社那個孩子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我的意志無關  那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她生來就是負責「鎮魂歸神」的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗…果然這兒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信媽媽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…你拿的那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來  日本被稱為因言靈而豐饒的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:39.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（言靈：語言的靈力）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.35,0:24:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言伴隨著靈力這種想法並不是日本所固有的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.52,0:24:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就古希臘「Logos」的概念來看
